t. The light changes according to the current phase of the moon, beginning with a translucent blue during a full moon, adding a brighter white in quarters until the new moon, when the belfry is illuminated by a brilliant white light."},"team":null,"press":null,"photoCredit":null,"projectLeader":[{"name":"Etienne Gillabert","slug":"etienne-gillabert","primaryOffice":"Paris","id":"f6bce36d-59aa-5cc3-9e5e-bffdb9adc158"}],"metadata":{"tags":[]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"bethune"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1395536887","143701507"],"slicesMap":{}}